'''Captain Henderson''' is a fire captain with [[Seattle Fire Department]].

==History==
Henderson came to station 19 with [[Natasha Ross|Chief Ross]] after Sullivan told her he suspected [[Sean Beckett]] of drinking on the job. They went into Beckett's office, where they explained that they were investigating some of his recent calls and a claim that he was drinking on the job. Henderson accompanied him to the bathroom so he could provide a sample of his urine for testing.

==Career==
He is a captain in the [[Seattle Fire Department]], working in the Professional Standards Unit.
